How do we work?
\"Business Diplomat: Uzbekistan\" consists of five consecutive levels, each containing a step-by-step provision of a knowledge base. Each level includes a carefully planned program with a trip to one of the developed countries of the world, designed to fully immerse participants in the local business culture, environment, traditions, mentality, and values of the host country.
